WEBVTT

00:03.775 --> 00:07.450
<i>It's another
sunny day in Indiana, folks!</i>

00:07.512 --> 00:11.255
<i>It's 90 degrees and climbing.</i>

00:11.316 --> 00:12.818
<i>So throw your kids in a lake,</i>

00:12.884 --> 00:15.296
<i>because it's going
to be a hot one!</i>

00:15.353 --> 00:17.333
<i>All right, now we're going
to try to beat the heat</i>

