for some scierrific fun.</i>

01:07.572 --> 01:08.812
Hey, where's your brother?

01:10.908 --> 01:12.820
You're going to look up
from that tiny little screen

01:12.844 --> 01:14.721
and your entire summer
is going to be gone.

01:14.779 --> 01:16.417
